hadiths[205]{hadithnumber,text}:
1433,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : dastoor key mutabiq musalman key musalman par chhe haq hain. jab us sey miley to salam kahey , jab wo usey dawat dey to uski dawat qubul karey , jab usey chheenk aaye to usey dua dey , jab wo bimar ho jaey to uski bimar pursi karey , jab wo faut ho jaey to uskey janaazey key sath jaey aur uskey liye wohi kuchh pasand karey jo apney liye pasand karta hai."
1434,"Hazrat abu-Masood Aqba bin Amr Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : musalman key zimmey musalman key chaar kaam hain : jab usey chheenk aaye to usey dua dey , jab wo usey dawat dey to qubul karey , jab wo faut ho jaey to (uskey janaazey mein) hazir ho aur jab wo bimar ho jaey to uski iyaadat karey."
1435,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen musalman key musalman par huquq mein shamil hain : salam ka jawab dena, dawat qubul karna, janaazey mein hazir hona, bimar ki iyaadat karna aur jab chheenkney wala Allah ki tareef karey (Alhamdulillah kahey) to usey dua dena (Yar-hamukallah kehna)."
1436,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) pedal chal kar meri iyaadat key liye tashrif laye jabke main banu Salma key mohalley mein tha."
1437,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) teen din key baad hi bimar ki iyaadat farmatey they."
1438,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mareez key paas jao to usey zindagi ki ummid dilao, us sey (taqdir ka faisla to) kuchh nahin talta lekin bimar ka dil khush ho jata hai."
1439,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bimar ki iyaadat key liye tashrif ley gaey to us sey farmaya : tumhara kis chiz ko ji chahta hai? usney kaha : gehun ki roti ko ji chahta hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis kisi key paas gehun ki roti ho, wo apney bhai key paas bhejey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab kisi ka mareez kisi chiz ki khahish karey to wo usey khila dey."
1440,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bimar key paas uski iyaadat key liye tashrif ley gaey. aap ney farmaya : tumhara kisi chiz ko ji chahta hai? kya ka'ak ki khahish hai? usney kaha : ji haan , chunanche Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney usey ka'ak (eik khas qism ki roti) mangwaa di."
1441,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : jab to kisi mareez key paas jaey to usey keh ke terey liye dua karey kyonkey uski dua farishton ki dua ki tarah hai."
1442,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke aap ney farmaya : jo shakhs apney musalman bhai key paas iyaadat key liye aata hai to wo mareez key paas aa kar bethney tak jannat key phal chuntaa aata hai. jab wo beth jata hai to is par rehmat saya daale hoti hai. agar (iyaadat) subah key waqt ho to Sham tak sattar hazar farishtey usey duayen detey rehtey hain aur agar Sham ka waqt ho to subah tak sattar hazar farishtey usey duayen detey rehtey hain."
1443,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi mareez ki iyaadat karta hai to usey aasman sey eik aawaz deney wala (farishta) aawaz deta hai : to bhi pak (aur achchha) hai aur tera chalna bhi pak hai aur tu ney jannat mein ghar bana liya."
1444,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney marney walon ko ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ ) ki talqin karo."
1445,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney marney walon ko ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ ) ki talqin karo."
1446,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney marney walon ko in alfaz ki talqin karo : (لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ الْحَلِيمُ الْكَرِيمُ , سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَرْشِ الْعَظِيمِ , الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ), ''Allah key siwa koi mabood nahin jo burdbaar aur karim hai, paak hai Allah jo arshe azeem ka Malik hai. sab taarifein Allah key liye hain, jo tamam jahano ka paalne-wala hai.'' Sahaba ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! zindon key liye ye zikr kaisa hai? farmaya : ziyada achchha, ziyada umda."
1447,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum bimar key paas jao. ya farmaya : marney waley key paas jao to achchhi baat kaho kyonkey tum jo kuchh (us waqt) kehtey ho, farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain.  (Ummul-mominin ney farmaya) jab abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum kaho (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي وَلَهُ , وَأَعْقِبْنِي مِنْهُ عُقْبًى حَسَنَةً), ''aey Allah ! mujhey aur usey bakhsh dey aur mujhey iska achchha badal ata farma.'' Ummul-mominin ney farmaya : mainey yehi dua ki to Allah Taala ney mujhey un sey behtar (khaawind) ata farmaya diya, yani Allah key Rasool Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)."
1448,Hazrat Maaqil bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Sura Yaseen key barey mein farmaya : usey apney faut honey walon key paas padha karo.
1449,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kaab bin Malik apney walid key barey mein bayan farmatey hain ke jab Hazrat Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt aaya (aur maut key aasaar zahir honey lagey) to Hazrat Bara bin Ma'roor (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti Hazrat Umme Bishr (Raziallahu anha) unkey paas aayen aur kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman (Kaab bin Malik) ! agar (aalame-arwaah mein) falan sey (Hazrat Bishr (Raziallahu anhu) sey) aap ki mulaqat ho to usey mera salam keh dijiyega, unhoney kaha : Umme Bishr ! Allah aap ki maghfirat kerey. hamein itni fursat kahan hogi? Umme Bishr (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye irshad Mubarak nahin suna : mominon ki roohen sabz (hare) parindon mein hain, jannat key darakhton sey (phal) khati hain.  unhoney kaha : haan (ye to suna hai). unhoney kaha : mera bhi yehi matlab hai."
1450,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Munkadir (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) ki wafat ka waqt tha to main uskey paas gaya aur mainey kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam keh dijiyega."
1451,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye jabke unkey paas unka eik rishte-daar tha jis par maut ki sakhti taari thi. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka ranj dekha to farmaya : Aaisha ! apney rishte-daar par gham na karo, ye bhi uski nekiyon mein sey hai."
1452,Hazrat Barida bin Haseeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : momin peshani key paseeney key sath martaa hai.
1453,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kiya : banda logon ko pehchaan'na kab chhod deta hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab wo (aakhirat ki chizon ya maut key farishton) ka mushaahida kar leta hai."
1454,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) (ki maiyat) key paas aaye to un ki aankhen khuli thin, aap ney un ki aankhen band kar den aur farmaya : jab rooh qabz ki jati hai to nazar uska taaqqub (peechha) karti hai."
1455,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum apney faut honey walon key paas mojud ho to (un ki) aankhen band kar diya karo kyonkey nazar bhi rooh key peechey peechey jati hai aur achchhi baat kaho kyonkey (us waqt) ghar waley jo kuchh kehtey hain, farishtey is par Aameen kehtey hain."
1456,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ko un ki wafat key baad bosa diya. goya main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key rukhsaaron par aansu behtey dekh rahi hun."
1457,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) aur Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat key baad aap ko bosa diya.
1458,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Nusaiba binte Kaab Ansaariya) (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahab-zaadi Hazrat Umme kulsoom (Raziallahu anha) ko ghusl dey rahi thin ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye, aap ney farmaya : usey pani aur beeri key patton key sath teen baar ya paanch baar ghusl do, agar zarurat mehsus ho to us sey ziyada baar ghusl dey dena aur aakhiri baar ghusl detey waqt pani mein kaafur ya farmaya : thoda sa kaafur dal lena aur jab tum farigh ho jao to mujhey ittilaah dena. hamney (ghusl deney sey) farigh ho kar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ittilaah di to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna teh-band hamari taraf phenk diya aur farmaya : isey uskey jism sey muttasil pehna do."
1459,Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey yehi hadees dusri sanad sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. is mein ye alfaz hain (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : )  isey taaq baar ghusl do. aur ye alfaz bhi hain : isey teen baar ya paanch baar ghusl do. aur ye alfaz bhi hain : iski daain janib sey aur wuzu key aaza (angon) sey ghusl dena shuru karo. aur is mein ye bhi hai ke Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : hamney unkey baalon ko kanghi kar key teen laten bana den.
1460,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey farmaya : apni raan zahir na karo aur kisi zinda ya murde ki raan ko na dekho."
1461,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey mardon ko wo log ghusl den jo qabil aitimad hon. (taake agar maiyat key barey mein koi aisi chiz malum ho jis ka zahir karna munasib nahin to wo usey raz rakh saken)."
1462,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney maiyat ko ghusl diya, kafan diya, khushbu lagai aur usey uthaya (qabristaan ko ley jatey huye uski chaar pai ko kandhaa diya), uska janaza padha, uski jo chiz nazar aai (jo zahir karney key qabil na ho) usey zahir na kiya, wo gunahon sey is tarah pak saaf ho jata hai jis tarah apni maa key yahan paida honey key din (gunahon sey pak saaf) tha."
1463,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs maiyat ko ghusl dey wo khud bhi ghusl kerey."
1464,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : agar mujhey pehley wo khayal aa jata jo baad mein aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyan) hi ghusl detin."
1465,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Baqee sey aaye to dekha ke merey sar mein dard ho raha hai aur main keh rahi hun : haaye mera sar ! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : balke Aaisha ! main (kehta hun) : haaye mera sar ! phir farmaya : tumhara kya nuqsan hai agar tumhari wafat mujh sey pehley ho gaee? (us surat mein) main khud tumharey liye (kafan dafn ka) ehtimam karunga, tumhen khud ghusl dunga, khud kafan pahnaaoonga, khud tumhara janaza padhunga aur khud dafn karunga."
1466,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghusl deney ka irada kiya to (ghar key) andar sey eik (naa-maaloom) aawaz deney waley ney aawaz di : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qamis na utaaro. (chunanche qamis samet ghusl diya gaya)."
1467,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghusl diya to unhoney wo chiz malum kerni chahi jo maiyat sey zahir huwa karti hai lekin aisi koi chiz mehsus na hui to unhoney farmaya : is pak hasti par mera baap qurban ho ! (aey Nabi ! ) aap zindagi mein bhi pak they, wafat key baad bhi pak hain."
1468,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab main faut ho jaun to mujhey merey kunwen ghars key pani ki saat mashkon sey ghusl dena."
1469,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen safed Yamni kapdon (chaadron) mein kafan diya gaya, un mein na qamis thi na amaamaa. Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey kiya gaya : baaz log kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dhaari daar chaadaron mein kafan diya gaya tha. Ummul-mominin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : log dhaari daar chadaren laye they lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko un mein kafan nahin diya gaya."
1470,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen safed sahwali chaadaron mein kafan diya gaya."
1471,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko teen kapdon mein kafan diya gaya. eik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wo qamis jisey aap wafat key waqt pehney huye they aur Najraani chaadaron ka eik joda."
1472,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumharey behtareen kapdey safed hain, lihaza apney mardon ko un mein kafan diya karo aur khud bhi pahno."
1473,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : behtareen kafan joda hai."
1474,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi apney bhai key maamlat ka nigraan baney to usey achchha kafan dey."
1475,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farzand Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey iskey kafan mein (puri tarah) na lapetna, jab tak main isey dekh na lun. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas aa kar un par jhuk gaey aur ro padey."
1476,"Hazrat Bilal bin Yahya (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) key aqaarib mein sey koi faut ho jata to wo farmatey : kisi ko uski ittilaa na karna, main darta hun ke ye bhi naey (aelan) mein shamil na ho. mainey apney in dono kanon sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maut key aelan sey mana kartey suna hai."
1477,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : janaazey ko jaldi (qabristaan ki taraf) ley jaya karo, agar maiyat nek hai to tum usey bhalai ki taraf ley ja rahey ho, agar dusri surat hai to eik buri chiz ka bojh apni gardanon sey utaar rahey ho."
1478,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs janaza uthaey (kandhaa dey), usey chahiye ke chaar-paai chaaron taraf sey (baari-baari) uthaey. kyonkey ye sunnat hai. uskey baad agar chahey to mazeed sawab hasil kar ley, chahey to rehney dey."
1479,Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey riwayat kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik janaza dekha jisey badi tezi sey liye ja rahey they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : itminan sey chalo .
1480,"Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney janaazey key sath kuch logon ko janweron par sawar ho kar jatey dekha to farmaya : kya tum log haya nahin kartey ke Allah key farishtey to pedal chal rahey hain aur tum sawar ho?"
1481,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : sawar janaazey key peechey chaley aur pedal jahan chahey (aagey, peechey, daain ya baain)."
1482,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ko janaazey key aagey chaltey dekha hai."
1483,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman Raziallahu anhum janaazey key aagey chaltey they."
1484,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : janaazey key peechey chala jata hai, janaza kisi key peechey nahin chalta , jo us sey aagey chaley wo uskey sath nahin ."
1485,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain aur Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, un dono ney kaha : eik janaazey mein hum Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath rawana huye . aap ney dekha ke kuch afrad ney (odhney wali) chadaren utaar phenki hain aur sirf qameesein pehan kar chal rahey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya tum jahiliyat ka amal ikhtiyar kar rahey ho? kya tum jahiliyat key kaam sey mushaabihat ikhtiyar kartey ho? mera ji chahta hai ke tumhen aisi bad dua dun ki tumhari soorten tabdeel ho jaeyn . chunanche unhoney apni chadaren odh lin aur dobara ye ghalati nahin ki."
1486,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab janaza tayyar ho jaey to takheer na karo ."
1487,"Hazrat abu-Barda (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jab Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ka waqt aaya to unhoney wasiyat kartey huye farmaya : merey sath (khushbu sulganey wali) angeethi na ley jana. haazirin ney kaha : kya aap ney is masley mein koi hadees suni hai? farmaya : haan , Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai."
1488,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis ka janaza so musalman padhein , usey bakhsh diya jaeyga."
1489,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Kureb (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ka eik beta faut ho gaya . unhoney mujhey farmaya : Kureb ! uth kar dekho ! kya merey betey (ka janaza padhney) key liye koi aaya hai? mainey kaha : ji haan . farmaya : tera bhala ho, terey khayal mein kitney afrad hain? chaalis to hongey? mainey kaha : nahin, balke us sey bhi ziyada hain. farmaya : to merey betey ko (namaz janaza key liye) ley chalo. main gawahi deta hun ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : jo chaalis momin kisi momin key haq mein dua keren, Allah un ki sifarish qubul farma leta hai."
1490,"Hazrat Malik bin Hubaira (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke (unki mojudgi mein) jab koi janaza laya jata aur wo mehsus kartey ke uskey sath aaney walon ki tadaad kam hai to unhen teen safon mein taqseem kar detey, phir janaza padhatey aur farmatey ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis maiyat ka janaza musalmanon ki teen safein ada karen. uskey liye (maghfirat ya jannat) wajib ho jati hai."
1491,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra, logon ney uski tareef ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. phir eik aur janaza guzra, uskey barey mein buri raey zahir ki gaee to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee . arz kya gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney uskey haq mein bhi farmaya : wajib ho gaee aur iskey haq mein bhi farmaya : wajib ho gaee. (uska kya matlab hai?) farmaya : logon ki gawahi (aur uskey natijey mein jannat hai ya jahannam) momin zamin mein Allah key gawah hain."
1492,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra , uski achi aadaton ki wajeh sey uski tareef ki gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee. phir log eik aur janaza ley kar guzrey to uski buri aadaton ki wajeh sey uskey barey mein buri raey zahir ki gaee to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wajib ho gaee, tum log zamin mein Allah key gawah ho."
1493,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub Fazari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik khatoon ka janaza padha jo nifaas key dinon mein faut ho gaee thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski kamar key muqabil khadey huye.
1494,"Hazrat Abu-Ghalib (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhoney eik mard ka janaza padhaya to uskey sar key muqabil khadey huye, phir eik aurat ka janaza laya gaya, haazirin ney kaha : abu-Hamza ! ( Anas bin Malik) iska janaza padha dijiye to aap chaarpai key beech key muqabil khadey huye (aur janaza padhaya .) Hazrat Alaa bin Ziyad (Adwii) (Rahimahullah) ney arz kya : abu-Hamza ! kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah kartey dekha hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mard key janazey mein is tarah (sar key barabar) khadey huye they jis tarah aap khadey huye hain aur aurat key janazey mein is tarah (kamar key muqabil) khadey huye they jis tarah aap khadey huye hain? Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan . Hazrat Alaa (Rahimahullah) ney hamari taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : (ye masla) yad kar lo ."
1495,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney namaze-janaza mein Sura Fatiha padhi.
1496,"Hazrat Umme shareek ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen namaze-janazey mein Sura Fatiha padhney ka hukm diya."
1497,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna ke aap ney farmaya : jab tum maiyat ki namaz (janaza) padho to uskey liye khulus sey dua karo ."
1498,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab janazey ki namaz padhatey to yun farmatey : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِحَيِّنَا وَمَيِّتِنَا وَشَاهِدِنَا وَغَائِبِنَا وَصَغِيرِنَا وَكَبِيرِنَا وَذَكَرِنَا وَأُنْثَانَا اللَّهُمَّ مَنْ أَحْيَيْتَهُ مِنَّا فَأَحْيِهِ عَلَى الإِسْلاَمِ وَمَنْ تَوَفَّيْتَهُ مِنَّا فَتَوَفَّهُ عَلَى الإِيمَانِ اللَّهُمَّ لاَ تَحْرِمْنَا أَجْرَهُ وَلاَ تُضِلَّنَا بَعْدَهُ)aey Allah ! hamarey zindon, murdon, hazir, ghaaieb, chhoton, badon, muzakkar aur muannas (sab) ki maghfirat farma dey. aey Allah ! hum mein sey jisey to zinda rakhey , usey Islam par zinda rakhna aur jisey faut karey uska khatima eman par karna . aey Allah ! us ( janey waley) key ajr sey hamen mehroom na karna aur uskey baad hamen gumrah na kar dena ."
1499,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik musalman ka janaza padha to mainey aap ko yun farmatey suna : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنَّ فُلاَنَ بْنَ فُلاَنٍ فِى ذِمَّتِكَ وَحَبْلِ جِوَارِكَ فَقِهِ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْقَبْرِ وَعَذَابِ النَّارِ وَأَنْتَ أَهْلُ الْوَفَاءِ وَالْحَقِّ فَاغْفِرْ لَهُ وَارْحَمْهُ إِنَّكَ أَنْتَ الْغَفُورُ الرَّحِيمُ ) aey Allah! falan ka beta falan terey supurd aur teri hifazat mein hai, usey qabr ki aazmaaish aur aag key azab sey mehfooz rakhna to wafaa aur haq wala hai, uski bakhshish farma dey aur is par rehmat farma , beshak to bakhshney wala , reham karney wala hai."
1500,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap ney eik Ansari aadmi ka janaza padhaya. mainey suna ke aap farma rahey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلَيْهِ وَاغْفِرْ لَهُ وَارْحَمْهُ وَعَافِهِ وَاعْفُ عَنْهُ وَاغْسِلْهُ بِمَاءٍ وَثَلْجٍ وَبَرَدٍ وَنَقِّهِ مِنَ الذُّنُوبِ وَالْخَطَايَا كَمَا يُنَقَّى الثَّوْبُ الأَبْيَضُ مِنَ الدَّنَسِ وَأَبْدِلْهُ بِدَارِهِ دَارًا خَيْرًا مِنْ دَارِهِ وَأَهْلاً خَيْرًا مِنْ أَهْلِهِ وَقِهِ فِتْنَةَ الْقَبْرِ وَعَذَابَ النَّارِ ) aey Allah ! is par rehmat farma , uski maghfirat farma , is par reham kar , usey aafiyat dey, usey maaf kar dey , usey pani , barf aur olon sey dho dal , usey gunahon sey is tarah pak kar dey , jaisey safed kapdey ko mail kuchail sey saaf kya jata hai. usey uskey ghar key badley uskey ghar sey behtar ghar aur uskey kunbey sey behtar kunba ata farma aur usey qabr ki aazmaaish sey aur aag key azab sey mehfooz farma. Hazrat Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : is maqam par mera ji chaha ke kaash! mein us (faut shuda) aadmi ki jagah hota ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey liye ye dua farmatey .)"
1501,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney hamen kisi chiz mein itni chhoot nahin di, jitni namaz janaza mein di hai. yani uskey liye waqt ki had muqarrar nahin ki."
1502,Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usman bin mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaz janaza ada farmaai aur chaar takbeerein kahin.
1503,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Ibrahim bin Muslim hijri (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Sahabi Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein un ki eik beti ka janaza padha . unhoney uskey janaazey mein chaar takbeerein kahin . chauthi takbir key baad wo kuch arsa thehrey . farmatey hain : mainey safon key atraaf sey logon ko subhan Allah kehtey suna . unhoney salam pher kar kaha : kya tumhara khayal tha ke paanch takbeerein keh dunga? haazirin ney kaha : hamen to yehi khatra mehsus huwa tha. unhoney farmaya : main to aisey nahin karney laga tha lekin Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaar takbeerein keh kar thodi der thehertey they aur jo kuch Allah Taala chahta wo kehtey (munasib dua padhtey), phir salam phertey they."
1504,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (namaz janaza mein) chaar takbeerein kahin.
1505,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin abi Leila (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) hum logon ki namaz janaza mein chaar takbeerein kaha kartey they. eik janazey mein unhoney paanch takbeerein kahin. mainey (uskey mutalliq) sawal kya to farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi isi tarah (paanch) takbeerein kaha kartey they."
1506,Hazrat Kasir bin Abdullah bin Amr bin Auf (Rahimahullah) apney walid sey aur wo unkey dada sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (namaz janaza mein) paanch takbeerein kahin.
1507,"Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : bachey ki namaz janaza padhi jaey."
1508,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab bacha paidaish key waqt (roey to) uskey faut honey par uska janaza padha jaey aur uski virasat taqseem ki jaey ."
1509,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney bachon ka janaza padha karo, wo tumharey pesh ro hain."
1510,"Hazrat Ismail bin abu-Khalid (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : kya aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key saahibzaadey Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha hai? unhoney kaha : wo to bachpan hi mein faut ho gaey they. agar taqdir ye hoti ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad koi aur Nabi ho to aap key (ye) farzand zinda rehtey. lekin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key baad koi Nabi nahin ."
1511,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farzand Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unka janaza padha aur farmaya : uskey liye jannat main eik doodh pilaney wali muqarrar hai aur agar wo zinda rehta to Nabi Siddiq hota aur agar wo zinda rehta to uskey mamu qibti azad ho jatey, phir kisi qibti ko ghulam na banaya jata ."
1512,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farzand Hazrat Qasim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Hazrat Khadeeja (Raziallahu anha) ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! ( meri chhaatiyon mein) Qasim ka doodh bahut utar aaya hai, kaash! Allah Taala usey itni zindagi deta ke doodh pilaney ki muddat puri ho jati to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : uski doodh peeney ki muddat jannat mein puri hogi . ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! agar mujhey ye baat malum ho jaey to is par mera gham kuch halka ho jaey . Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar to chahey to main Allah sey dua karun aur wo tujhey uski aawaz suna dey . unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool ! main Allah aur uskey Rasool ki baat par yaqin rakhti hun ."
1513,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Uhud ki jang key din shohda ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas laya gaya. aap un mein sey das-das afrad ka janaza ada karney lagey. Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) jahan they wahin rahey (un ki maiyat samney rahi), dusron ki maiyetein utha li jati thin aur Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki maiyat jaisey thi, wesay hi (samney) padi rehti thi ."
1514,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Uhad key shohda mein sey do-do teen-teen aadmiyon ko eik hi kapdey sey dhanp detey they, phir farmatey : un mein sey kisko Quran ziyada yad hai? jab un mein sey kisi eik ki taraf ishara kya jata to lahad mein usey aagey rakhtey aur farmatey : main unkey haq mein gawah hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen unkey khoon sey lathpath hi dafn karney ka hukm diya, na unka janaza padha, na unhen ghusl diya gaya."
1515,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-Uhad key shaheedon key barey mein hukm diya ke un sey loha (hathiyar, maslan : zireh, dhaal waghera (aur chamda) chamdey key malboosaat (utaar diye jaeyn aur unhen khoon samet unkey kapdon hi mein dafn kar diya jaey."
1516,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jange-Uhad key shaheedon ko shahadat key maqamat par wapis ley janey ka hukm diya jabke unhen Madina laya ja chuka tha."
1517,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney masjid mein janaza padha, uskey liye kuch nahin."
1518,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qism hai Allah ki! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Baiza (Raziallahu anhuma) key betey Hazrat Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) ka janaza masjid hi mein padha tha. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki hadees ziyada qawi hai."
1519,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Johni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : teen oqaat aisey hain jin sey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen mana farmatey they ke un (oqaat) mein namaz padhein ya un mein apney faut huey logon ko dafn karen : jab suraj tuloo ho raha ho aur theek dopahar ( zawal) key waqt yahan tak key suraj dhal jaey aur jab suraj ghurub honey key qarib ho yahan tak key (puri tarah) ghurub ho jaey ."
1520,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik shakhs ko raat key waqt qabr mein utara aur uski qabr mein chiragh ley gaey .
1521,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney faut honey walon ko raat ko dafn na karo, siwaye uskey ke tumhen koi majburi ho."
1522,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : apney faut honey walon ka janaza raat ko bhi padho aur din ko bhi ."
1523,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Abdullah bin Ubai mara to uskey betey ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! mujhey apni qamis inayat farmaiye, main us ( qamis) mein usey kafnaaunga to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey us (ka janaza tayyar honey) ki ittilaa dena . jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska janaza padhney ka irada farmaya to Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : ye aap key laaiq nahin . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey do chizon mein sey eik key intikhaab ka ikhtiyar hai) kyonkey Allah Taala ney farmaya hai : (اسْتَغْفِرْ لَهُمْ أَوْ لاَ تَسْتَغْفِرْ لَهُمْ) aap unkey liye bakhshish maangen ya na maangen ( barabar hai.) tab Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farmaai : ( وَلاَ تُصَلِّ عَلَى أَحَدٍ مِنْهُمْ مَاتَ أَبَدًا وَلاَ تَقُمْ عَلَى قَبْرِهِ ) (aey Nabi !) un mein sey jo mar jaey aap uski namaz ( janaza (hergiz na padhein aur na kabhi uski qabr par khadey hon. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees sey ye masla bhi samajh mein aata hai ke kisi zinda shakhs ka qabr par khadey hona (aur maiyat key liye dua karna) neki hai."
1524,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Madina mein munafiqon ka sardar ( Abdullah bin Ubai) mar gaya . usney (marney sey pehley) wasiyat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski namaaze-janaza padhaein aur apni qamis Mubarak ka kafan pahnaaein, chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski namaz janaza padhi , apni qamis mein usey kafnaya aur uski qabr par) uskey haq mein dua karney key liye (khadey ho gaey to Allah Taala ney ye aayat nazil farma di : ( وَلاَ تُصَلِّ عَلَى أَحَدٍ مِنْهُمْ مَاتَ أَبَدًا وَلاَ تَقُمْ عَلَى قَبْرِهِ ) ( التوبہ : ۸۴ ( , aey Nabi ! un mein sey jo mar jaey aap hergiz uski namaze-janaza (na padhein aur na) kabhi uski qabr par khadey hon ."
1525,"Hazrat Waasila Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har maiyat ka janaza padho aur har ameer ki qiyaadat mein jihad karo ."
1526,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sathiyon mein sey eik sahab zakhmi ho gaey. unhen zakham sey takleef hui, wo reng kar teer key phal tak pahuncha, aur uskey zariey sey apney aap ko zibeh kar liya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uski namaz janaza na padhi. Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhuma) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney tanbih key tor par aisa kya."
1527,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik siyah-faam khatoon masjid ki safai kya karti thin, wo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko nazar na aain to chand din baad unkey mutalliq daryaft farmaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya gaya ke wo faut ho gaee hain. aap ney farmaya : tum ney mujhey ittila kyon na di ? phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unki qabr par tashrif ley gaey aur namaze-janaza ada ki."
1528,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) key badey bhai Hazrat Yazeed bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath bahar gaey jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baqee (key qabristaan) mein pahunchey to aap ko eik naee qabr nazar aai, Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney uskey barey mein daryaft farmaya. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : falan khatoon hai (ye unki qabr hai.) aap ney usey pehchan liya. farmaya : tum ney mujhey uski (wafat ki) ittilaa kyon na di? unhoney kaha : aap dopahar ko aaram farma rahey they aur aap rozey sey they to hamen ye baat achi na lagi ke aap ko takleef den . aap ney farmaya : yun na kya karo. mujhey (tum sey dobara aisey amal ki) hergiz khabar na miley . jab tak main tumharey darmiyan ( zinda) mojud hun. tum mein sey jo koi bhi faut ho, mujhey zarur ittila kya karo kyonkey meri dua unkey liye rehmat ka baais hai.' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabr par tashrif ley gaey, hamney aap key peechey saf bana li aur aap ney is par chaar takbeerein kahin."
1529,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhuma) apney walid Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : eik siyah faam khatoon ki wafat ho gaee , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski ittilaa na di gaee . (baad mein) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us ( ki wafat) ka ilm huwa to farmaya : tum ney mujhey uski wafat ki ittilaa kyon na di ? phir aap ney Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum sey farmaya is ( ki namaz janaza) key liye safein banao . tab aap ney uska janaza padha ."
1530,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik aadmi faut ho gaya .) wafat sey pehley bimari key dinon mein) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uski iyaadat kya kartey they. Sahaba kiram ney usey raat hi ko dafn kar diya . jab subh hui to unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya . aap ney farmaya : mujhey khabar karney main tumhen kya cheez rukawat thi? unhoney kaha : raat ka waqt tha aur andhera bhi tha to hamney aap ko takleef dena pasand na kya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us shakhs ki qabr par ja kar namaz janaza ada ki."
1531,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik qabr par maiyat ki tadfeen key baad namaaz janaza padhi .
1532,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida (Rahimahullah) apney walid Hazrat Barida bin Huseb (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik maiyat ka janaza uskey dafn kiye janey key baad ada kya."
1533,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik siyah faam khatoon masjid mein jhaadu diya karti thi . eik raat wo faut ho gaee . subh ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski wafat ki ittilaa di gaee . aap ney farmaya : tum ney mujhey (us waqt) kyon na uski wafat ki ittilaa di? phir aap Sahaba ko sath ley kar nikley aur uski qabr par ja khadey huye . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aur aap key peechey tamam logon ney us par) namaz janaza ki) takbeerein kahin aur uskey liye duayen kin (namaz janaza padhi), phir wapis aa gaey."
1534,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Najaashi faut ho gaya hai.' ( uskey baad) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sathi baqee mein tashrif ley gaey . aap ney apney peechey hamari safein banaain, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (khud) aagey badhey aur chaar takbeerein kahin."
1535,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara bhai Najaashi faut ho gaya hai, uska janaza padh lo. Sahabi bayan kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur hamney aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz (janaza) ada ki. main dusri saf mein tha. aap ney do safein bana kar uska janaza padhaya ."
1536,"Hazrat majmaa bin jaariya Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tumhara bhai Najaashi faut ho gaya hai, utho uska janaza padho lo . to hamney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key peechey do safein bana lein."
1537,Hazrat Huzefa bin Usaid ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko ley kar nikley aur farmaya : apney eik bhai ka janaza padho jo tumharey ilaqey sey bahar faut ho gaya hai. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : wo kon hai? farmaya : Najaashi.
1538,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Najaashi (Rahimahullah) ka janaza padha to chaar takbeerein kahin.
1539,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney janaazey ki namaz padhi uskey liye eik qeeraat sawab hai aur jisney intizar kya yahan tak key us ( key dafn) sey faraaghat ho jaey, uskey liye do qeeraat sawab hai. Sahaba ney kaha : do qeeraat kaisey hotey hain? aap ney farmaya : do pahadon key barabar ."
1540,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney janaazey ki namaz padhi uskey liye eik qeeraat (sawab) hai aur jo uskey dafn tak hazir raha uskey liye do qeeraat (sawab) hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey qeeraat key mutalliq puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : Uhad ( pahad) key barabar ."
1541,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney janaazey ki namaz padhi , uskey liye eik qeeraat (sawab) hai aur jo hazir raha yahan tak key ( maiyat ko) dafn kya jaey, uskey liye ( sawab key ( do qeeraat hain. qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) ki jaan hai, (sawab ka) qeeraat us ahad sey bhi bada hai."
1542,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Aamir bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum janaza dekho to uskey liye khadey ho jao yahan tak key wo aagey guzar jaey ya ( zamin par) rakh diya jaey .
1543,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey eik janaza guzra to aap khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : khadey ho jao , maut ki eik ghabrahat (aur pareshani) hoti hai."
1544,"Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) janaza dekh kar khadey huye to hum bhi khadey ho gaey, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey to hum bhi beth gaey ."
1545,"Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi janaazey key sath jatey to maiyat ko qabr mein rakhey janey tak na bethtey (eik baar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik Yahudi aalim mila , usney kaha : aey Muhammad ! hum bhi isi tarah kartey hain. tab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bethney lagey aur farmaya : un ki mukhalifat karo ."
1546,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey ( bistar par) nazar na aaye . dekha to aap baqeee (qabristaan) mein they. ( wahan) aap ney farmaya : ( السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ دَارَ قَوْمٍ مُؤْمِنِينَ أَنْتُمْ لَنَا فَرَطٌ وَإِنَّا بِكُمْ لاَحِقُونَ اللَّهُمَّ laa تَحْرِمْنَا أَجْرَهُمْ وَلاَ تَفْتِنَّا بَعْدَهُمْ ) aey momin logon ki basti walo ! tum par salamti ho, tum hamarey pesh ro ho aur hum bhi tum sey aa milney waley hain. aey Allah ! hamen un ( par sabr) key sawab sey mehroom na rakhna aur un ( ki wafat) key baad hamen aazmaaish mein mubtala na karna ."
1547,"Hazrat Barida bin Huseb Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ko sikhaya kartey they ke wo jab qabristaan mein jaeyn ( to ye dua padhein , chunanche) un mein sey jo shakhs (qabristaan mein ja kar) dua karta , wo yun kehta : ( السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ أَهْلَ الدِّيَارِ مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَالْمُسْلِمِينَ وَإِنَّا إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ بِكُمْ لاَحِقُونَ نَسْأَلُ اللَّهَ لَنَا وَلَكُمُ الْعَافِيَةَ ) , tum par salamti ho, aey mominon aur musalmanon ki basti walo ! hum bhi insha Allah tum sey aa milney waley hain. hum Allah sey apney liye aur tumharey liye aafiyat ka sawal kartey hain."
1548,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik janaazey mein gaey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qibla ro ho kar beth gaey ."
1549,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum eik janaazey mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath gaey . hum qabr tak pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey aur hum bhi) badi khamoshi sey) beth gaey . goya hamarey saron par perindey hain."
1550,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab maiyat ko qabr mein dakhil kya jata to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey they : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى مِلَّةِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ ) , Allah key naam sey aur uskey Rasool ki millat par . Raaviye-hadees abu-Khalid ney eik riwayat mein ye alfaz bayan kiye hain : jab maiyat ko lahad mein rakha jata to aap farmatey : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى سُنَّةِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ ) , Allah key naam sey aur uskey Rasool key tareeqey key mutabiq . aur راوئ hadees Hisham ney apni riwayat mein yun bayan kya : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَفِى سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى مِلَّةِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ ) , Allah key naam sey , Allah ki raah mein aur Allah key Rasool ki millat par ."
1551,"Hazrat abu-Raafey (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko sar ki taraf sey qabr mein utara aur un ki qabr par pani chhidkaa ."
1552,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key jism Mubarak ko qibley ki taraf sey liya gaya aur utha kar qabr mein dakhil kar diye gaey.
1553,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik janaazey mein Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) key sath hazir tha. jab unhoney maiyat ko qabr mein rakha to farmaya : ( بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَفِى سَبِيلِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى مِلَّةِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ ) , Allah key naam sey , Allah ki raah mein aur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki millat par . jab lahad par kachchi iinetein lagana shuru ki gaeen to farmaya : ( اللَّهُمَّ أَجِرْهَا مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ وَمِنْ عَذَابِ الْقَبْرِ اللَّهُمَّ جَافِ الأَرْضَ عَنْ جَنْبَيْهَا وَصَعِّدْ رُوحَهَا وَلَقِّهَا مِنْكَ رِضْوَانًا ) , aey Allah ! usey shetan sey aur qabr key azab sey panah dey , aey Allah ! uskey pahluon sey) qabr ki) zamin ko door rakh , uski rooh ko buland kar aur usey apni khushnoodi nasib farma .) Saeed bin Musaiyab ney farmaya ( mainey kaha : ibne-Umar ! kya aap ney ye chiz Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai ya apni raey sey ye alfaz kahey hain? unhoney kaha : tab to main baaten bananey par qadir hun, ( nahin) balke ye chiz mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suni hai."
1554,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lahad ( baghli qabr) hamarey liye hai aur shaqq (sanduqi qabr) hamarey siwa dusron key liye hai."
1555,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : baghli qabr hamarey liye hai aur sanduqi qabr dusron key liye."
1556,"Hazrat Aamir bin Saad apney walid Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : merey liye lahad tayyar karna aur mujh par kachchi eintein lagana jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye kya gaya tha."
1557,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut huye, us waqt Madiney main eik aadmi lahad wali qabr banaya karta tha aur ek aadmi sidhi ( shaqq wali) qabr banata tha. Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney kaha : hum apney rab sey istikhaara kartey hain ( behtar chiz ki dua kartey hain (aur dono ko bula bhejtey hain jo peechey reh gaya, usey chhod dengey .) aur jo pehley aa gaya, wo apney tareeqey par qabr tayyar kar dega ( chunanche un dono ko pegham bheja gaya to lahad bananey wala pehley aa gaya, chunanche Sahaba Raziallahu anhum ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye baghli qabr tayyar karwaai."
1558,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka intiqal huwa to Sahaba Raziallahu anhum mein baghli ( lahad wali) ya sidhi ( shaqq wali) qabr key barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya . unhoney us barey mein behes ki yahan tak key un ki aawazen buland ho gaeen . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas zor sey na bolo , chahey aap zinda hon ya faut ho chukey hon, ya aisey hi deegar alfaz farmaaey, chunanche unhoney sidhi (shaqq wali) qabr bananey waley aur baghli ( lahad wali) qabr bananey waley dono ko bula bheja . baghli ( lahad wali) qabr bananey wala ( pehley) aa gaya . usney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye baghli ( lahad wali) qabr tayyar ki, phir Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dafn kar diya gaya ."
1559,"Hazrat Adraa Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main eik raat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki pehrey daari ki niyat sey hazir huwa , mainey dekha ke eik aadmi bahut buland aawaz sey tilawat kar raha hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye shakhs riya kaar hai. ( baad mein) jab Madina mein wo shakhs faut huwa aur Sahaba Raziallahu anhum us ko tayyar karney sey) ghusl aur kafan waghera sey) farigh huye aur uski chaar pai uthai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : is sey narmi karo, Allah Taala is par narmi karey , ye Allah aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat rakhta tha. , Raavi kehtey hain, aap ney uski qabr tayyar karwaai to farmaya : uski qabr kushada karo, Allah is par kushadgi farmaai . eik Sabab ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ko us ( ki wafat) ka bahut gham huwa hai. farmaya : haan , wo Allah sey aur uskey Rasool sey mohabbat rakhta tha. ,"
1560,"Hazrat Hisham bin Aamir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (qabren) kushada aur achchhi khodo."
1561,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney Hazrat Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ki qabr par (uskey sarhaaney) alamat key tor par eik bada patthar rakha.
1562,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ko choonaa gach karney sey mana farmaya."
1563,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabr par koi chiz likhney sey mana farmaya hai."
1564,Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabr par koi chiz taamir karney sey mana farmaya.
1565,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik maiyat ka janaza padha, phir uski qabr par aaye aur uskey sar ki taraf sey is par (mitti ki) teen lappein dalin."
1566,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey kisi ka angaarey par beth jana aur aag ka usey jala dena, uskey liye qabr par bethney sey behtar hai."
1567,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kisi musalman ki qabr par chalney key muqabley mein mujhey ye baat pasand hai ke main angaarey par ya talwaar par chalun ya apna joota apni taang sey si lun, (isi tarah) sare-baazaar qazaey-hajat (peshaab paakhaana) karna aur qabron key darmiyan qazaey-hajat (peshaab paakhaana) karna merey nazdik barabar hai."
1568,"Hazrat Bashir ibne Khasasiya (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath ja raha tha ke aap ney farmaya : aey ibne Khasasiya ! tujhey Allah sey kya shikwa hai (halanke tujhey ye maqam hasil ho gaya hai ke) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath chal raha hai? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey Allah Taala sey koi shikwa nahin. mujhey Allah ney har bhalai inayat farmaai hai. (isi beech mein) aap musalmanon ki qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : inhen bahut bhalai mil gaee. phir mushrikon ki qabron key paas sey guzrey to farmaya : ye bahut si bhalai sey mehroom reh gaey. achchha aap ki nigah aisey aadmi par padi jo qabron key darmiyan jooton samet chal raha tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey jooton waley ! inhen utaar dey. Imam Ibne-Maja ney apney ustad Muhammad bin Bashaar sey bayan kiya ke ibne Mehdi kehtey hain, Abdullah bin Usman kaha kartey they ye hadees umda hai aur iska Raavi Khalid bin Sameer Suqa (bharosemand) hai."
1569,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qabron ki ziyaarat kiya karo, ye tumhen aakhirat ki yad dahani karati hai."
1570,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ki ziyaarat ki ijazat di.
1571,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mainey tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat sey mana kiya tha, to (ab) un ki ziyaarat kiya karo kyonkey wo duniya sey be-raghbati paida karti hai aur aakhirat ki yad dilati hai."
1572,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apni walida ki qabr ki ziyaarat ki, aap khud bhi roey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki kaifiyat dekh kar jo (hazraat aap key sath) aap key ird-gird they, wo bhi aasunon se bhar gaey. tab aap ney farmaya : mainey apney Rab sey unkey liye (walida key liye) duaaey maghfirat ki ijazat talab ki to usney mujhey ijazat nahin di aur mainey apney Rab sey un ki qabr ki ziyaarat ki ijazat talab ki to usney mujhey ijazat dey di, isliye qabron ki ziyaarat kiya karo, ye tumhen maut ki yad dilaaeygi."
1573,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mera walid sila rehmi karta tha, aur is mein falan falan khubiyan thin, wo kahan hai? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jahannam mein hai. us ko ye jawab goya nagawar to guzra to kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap key walid kahan hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : to jahan bhi kisi mushrik ki qabr key paas sey guzrey to usey jahannam ki khush-khabri dey dey. baad mein us Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ney Islam qubul kar liya (baad mein ye waqia bayan kartey huye) usney kaha : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik mushkil kaam merey zimmey laga diya hai, jab bhi mera guzar kisi kafir ki qabr key paas sey hota hai, main usey jahannam ki khushkhabri deta hun."
1574,"Hazrat Hassan bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ki ba-kasrat ziyaarat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai."
1575,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ki ba-kasrat ziyaarat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai."
1576,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney qabron ki ba-kasrat ziyaarat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai.
1577,"Hazrat Umme Atiya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamein janaazon key sath janey sey mana kiya gaya hai lekin pukhta hukm nahin diya gaya."
1578,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to dekha kuchh khawatin bethi hain. farmaya : tum kyon bethi hui ho?unhoney kaha : janaazey ka intizar kar rahi hain. farmaya : kya ghusl do gi? unhoney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : (maiyat ki chaar pai ko) kandhaa dogi? unhoney kaha : ji nahin. farmaya : (maiyat ko) qabr mein utaarney walon key sath tum bhi utaarogi? unhoney kaha : ji nahin . farmaya : gunah ley kar, sawab sey mehroom ho kar wapis chali jao."
1579,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney aayate mubaraka (وَلاَ يَعْصِينَكَ فِى مَعْرُوفٍ ),''neki key kaam mein aap ki nafarmani nahin kerengi.'' ki wazahat kartey huye farmaya : nauha key barey mein hai."
1580,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Jareer (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney teiswin shehar mein khutba diya to us khutbey key doran mein ye bhi zikr farmaya ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney nauha karney sey mana farmaya hai."
1581,"Hazrat abu-Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nauha (dikhne wale) jahiliyat ka riwaaj hai. nauha karney wali agar tauba kiye baghair mar gaee to Allah Taala uskey liye tarkol key kapdey aur aag key sholey ki qamis tayyar karega."
1582,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat par nauha karna jahiliyat ka riwaaj hai. nauha karney wali agar tauba kiye baghair mar gaee to usey qiyamat key din us haal mein uthaya jaeyga ke uskey jism par tarkol ki qameesein hongi, phir un par aag key sholoon ki qamis pahnaai jaeygi."
1583,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us janaazey key sath janey sey mana farmaya hai jis key sath nauha karney wali aurat ho."
1584,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs gireban chaak karey aur rukhsaaron par tamaachey maarey aur jahiliyat ki tarah dikhne wala (nauha) kerey. wo hum mein sey nahin."
1585,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Asad bin Sehal bin Haneef) (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (izhare gham key liye) chehra nochne wali par, gireban chaak karney wali par, aur barbadi aur halakat pukarney wali par lanat farmaai hai."
1586,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed aur Hazrat Abu-Barda (Reh.) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ziyada bimar ho gaey to un ki biwi Hazrat Umme Abdulla (Raziallahu anha) buland aawaz sey roney lagin. Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko kuchh ifaaqa (faayda) huwa to farmaya : kya tujhey malum nahin ke main bhi us sey be-zaar hun jis sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bezari ka izhar farmaya hai? (is bimari sey pehley) wo unhen hadees sunaya kartey they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main us shakhs sey be-zaar hun jo (izhare-gham key liye) baal mundwaaey ya bayaan karey ya kapdey phaadey."
1587,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik janaazey mein shareek they. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney eik khatoon ko dekha (jo ro rahi thi) to usey buland aawaz sey mana kiya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : umr ! usey roney do, aakhon sey aansu behtey hain, dil ko gham pahuncha hai aur waqt ziyada nahin guzra (gham taza hai). Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : hamen abu-Bakar bin Abi Sheeba ney Affaan sey, unhoney Hammad bin Salma sey, unhoney Hisham bin Urawaa sey, unhoney Wahab bin Kaisaan sey, unhoney Muhammad bin Amr bin Ata sey, unhoney Salma bin Arzaq sey, unhoney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi (mazkoora baala) riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya."
1588,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik sahab-zaadi (Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha))  ka eik beta (Ali bin Abul-Aas bin Rabee (Raziallahu anhuma)) haalat naza' (jaan nikalne qareeb) mein tha. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pegham bheja ke tashrif laaeyn. Nabi (Alaihissalam) ney pegham bheja (ke Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko keh den : ),  Allah hi ka hai jo wo ley ley aur usi ka hai jo wo dey dey aur uskey paas har chiz ki eik muddat muqarrar hai, isliye (Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ko chahiye ke) wo sabr karen aur Allah sey sawab ki ummid rakhen. unhoney qism di (ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zarur tashrif laaeyn), chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uth khadey huye aap key sath main bhi tha aur Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal, Ubai-bin Kaab aur Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhum) bhi rawana huye jab hum unkey yahan pahunchey to bachchey ko Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchaya gaya jabke bachchey ki jaan uskey seeney mein thi (saans ukhad chuka tha malum hota tha aakhiri waqt hai) Raavi ney ghaaliban ye bhi kaha : yun lagta tha ke jaisiy purani mushk hai (jis tarah is mein pani harkat karta hai, is tarah saans mushkil sey aa raha tha) (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aasunon se bhar gaey. Hazrat Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ney (tajjub sey) kaha : Allah key Rasool ! ye kya? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye wo rehmat hai jo Allah Taala ney bani Adam mein rakhi hai aur Allah bhi apney un bandon par reham karta hai jo (doosron par) reham karney waley hotey hain."
1589,"Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key farzand Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ro padey. ta'ziyat karney waley eik sahaba, Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ya Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aap ki ye shaan hai ke aap Allah key haq ki azmat ka sab sey ziyada khayal rakhney waley hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aakhon sey aansu behtey hain, dil ghamgin hai, (lekin) hum wo alfaz nahin kahengey jin sey Allah naraz ho. agar ye baat na hoti ke ye (maut) eik sacha wada hai (jis sey mafar nahin) aur is wade ki chiz (maut) ki wajeh sey sab (aalim aakhirat mein) ikatthey honey waley hain aur baad wala bhi pehley waley key peechhey janey wala hai to aey Ibrahim ! hamein (ab) jitna gham huwa hai us sey kahin ziyada hota aur hum teri wajeh sey yaqinan ghamgin hain."
1590,"Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Hajash ney (apni phuphi) Hazrat Hamna binte Hajash (Raziallahu anha) key barey mein bayan farmaya ke (ghazwaae-uhad key moqey par) unhen kaha gaya : aap key bhai-jaan (Hazrat Abdullah bin hajash (Raziallahu anhu)) shaheed ho gaey. unhoney farmaya : Allah Taala un par rehmat farmaaey ( إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ ) (kuchh der baad) logon ney unhen kaha : aap key khawind (Hazrat Musab bin Umer (Raziallahu anhu) shaheed ho gaey. unkey munh sey nikla, haaye mera gham ! Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aurat ko khawind sey jo qalbi talluq hota hai wo aur kisi sey nahin hota."
1591,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabila banu Abdul-Ash'hal ki aurton key paas sey guzrey, wo jange uhad mein halak honey waley apney aqaarib par ro rahi thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lekin Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) par roney waliyan koi nahin. (ye sun kar) ansaar ki khawatin aa kar Hazrat Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) par roney lagin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bedaar huye to farmaya : afsos ! ye abhi wapis nahin gaeen. unhen hukm do ke wapis chali jaeyn aur aaj key baad kisi marney waley par na roeyn."
1592,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney marsiya-goii sey mana farmaya."
1593,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat par nauha kiya jaey to uski wajeh sey maiyat ko azab hota hai."
1594,"Hazrat Usaid bin Abu-Usaid (Rahimahullah) ney Hazrat Musa bin Abu-Musa Ash-ari sey, unhoney apney walid (Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) sey riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : zinda key roney sey faut shuda ko azab hota hai, jab wo (roney waley) kehtey hain : haaye mera bazu ! haaye mujhey libas deney wala ! haaye meri madad karney wala ! haaye wo pahad (jaisi azeem shakhsiyat) aur is tarah key alfaz kehtey hain to usey jhidka aur jhinjhodaa jata hai aur kaha jata hai : kya to (waaqaee) aisa hi hai? kya to aisa hi hai? Hazrat Usaid (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mainey kaha : Subhan Allah ! Allah Taala ney to farmaya hai : (وَلاَ تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌ وِزْرَ أُخْرَى), ''koi bojh uthaney wala kisi doosrey ka bojh nahin uthaeyga.'' Hazrat Musa (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : tera bhala ho ! main to tujhey ye bata raha hun ke abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ye hadees sunai hai (lekin tujhey yaqin nahin aata) kya tera khayal hai ke abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot baandha hai? ya tera ye khayal hai ke mainey abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) par jhoot baandhnaa hai?"
1595,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik Yahudi aurat mar gaee. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney un logon ko is par rotey huye suna to farmaya : iskey ghar waley is par ro rahey hain aur isey qabr mein azab ho raha hai."
1596,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : sabr ibtadaaey sadme key waqt hi hota hai."
1597,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah Taala farmata hai : aey Adam key betey ! agar ibtadaaey sadme key waqt to sabr karey aur husoole sawab ki niyat karey to main terey liye jannat sey kam sawab pasand nahin karunga."
1598,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhen Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ney hadees sunai ke unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai : jis musalman ko koi musibat pahunchti hai aur wo us pareshani mein Allah key hukm (ki taameel) ka sahara leta hai, yani kehta hai : (إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ اللَّهُمَّ عِنْدَكَ احْتَسَبْتُ مُصِيبَتِى فَأْجُرْنِى فِيهَا , وَعَوِّضْنِي مِنْهَا), ''hum Allah key hain aur usi ki taraf wapis janey waley hain. aey Allah ! main tujh sey apni musibat (par sabr) ka sawab chahta hun, mujhey iska ajr aur sawab ata farma aur iska badal ata farma.'' Allah taala us (musalman) ko us (musibat par sabr) ka sawab inayat farmata hai aur usey is (chhin janey waley nemat) sey behtar mutabadil (badla) ata farmata hai. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : jab Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to mujhey wo hadees yad aai jo unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sun kar mujhey sunai thi. tab mainey kaha : (إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ اللَّهُمَّ عِنْدَكَ احْتَسَبْتُ مُصِيبَتِى هَذِهِ فَأْجُرْنِى عَلَيْهَا), ''hum Allah hi key hain aur hum usi ki taraf wapis janey waley hain. aey Allah ! main tujh sey apni is musibat (par sabr) ka sawab chahti hun, to mujhey iska ajr aur sawab ata farma.'' jab mainey ye kehna chah : (وَعَوِّضْنِيى خَيْرًا مِنْهَا), ''mujhey iska behtar mutabadil ata farma.''to mainey dil mein socha : kya mujhey Hazrat abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) sey behtar mutabadil bhi mil sakta hai? phir mainey (dua key) ye alfaz bhi padh diye (aur hadees ki taameel mein ye dua mang hi li) to Allah ney mujhey abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) key badley Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dey diye aur meri musibat ka ajr bhi ata farma diya."
1599,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (aakhiri marz key dinon main eik din) wo darwaza khola ya parda hataayaa jo aap key aur (masjid mein namaz padhney waley) logon key darmiyan haael (rukaawat) tha. dekha to log Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaz padh rahey they. aap ney unhen is achchhey haal mein dekh kar Allah ka shukar ada kiya (ke Allah ki ibadat mein mashghool hain). aap ko ye ummid hui ke Allah Taala Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ki wafat) key baad bhi in ko aisey hi (achchhey) haal mein rakhega jo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mulaehiza farmaya , phir farmaya : aey logo ! jis shakhs ko. ya farmaya : jis momin ko koi musibat pahunchey to usey chahiye ke kisi doosrey ki (wafat ki) wajeh sey pahunchney wali musibat ka gham halka karney key liye meri (wafat ki) wajeh sey pahunchney wali musibat ko yad kar ley kyonkey meri ummat key kisi fard ko meri (wafat ki) musibat sey badh kar koi musibat nahin pahunch sakti."
1600,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisey koi musibat aai, (baad mein) phir usey wo musibat (dobara) yad aai to usney naey sirey sey (إِنَّا لِلَّهِ وَإِنَّا إِلَيْهِ رَاجِعُونَ) padh liya, agar-che us ko guzrey taweel (lamba) arsa guzar gaya ho, Allah Taala uskey liye itna hi sawab likheyga jitna (us din mila tha) jis din musibat aai thi."
1601,"Hazrat Amr bin Hazam (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo momin apney bhai ko kisi musibat par tasalli deta hai, Allah Taala usey qiyamat key din izzat afzaai ki poshaak ata farmaeyga."
1602,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi musibat zada ko tasalli dey, isey bhi us (musibat zada) key barabar sawab milega."
1603,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aadmi key teen bachchey faut ho jaeyn wo jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga magar qism puri karney key liye."
1604,"Hazrat Utba bin Abd Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap ney farmaya : jis musalman key teen bachchey faut ho jaeyn jo gunah ki umr ko na pahunchey hon, wo jannat key aathon darwazon par uska istaqbal kerengey, jis darwazey sey chahey (jannat mein) dakhil ho jaey."
1605,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jin do musalmanon (miyan biwi) key teen bachchey faut ho jaeyn jo gunah ki umr ko na pahunchey hon to Allah Taala un par rehmat kar key unhen jannat mein dakhil kar dega."
1606,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney teen bachchey aagey bhejey jo gunah ki umr ko na pahunchey hon, wo uskey liye jahannam sey bachao key liye eik mazbut rukawat bin jaeyngey. Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : mainey do bachchey aagey bhejey hain. aap ney farmaya : aur do bhi (jahannam sey hifazat ka baais bin jaeyngey). Qurra key sardar Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey eik bacha aagey bheja hai.  Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aur eik bhi (jahannam sey bachao ka baais hoga)."
1607,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey wo bachcha jo hamal me hi mar jaaey apney aagey bhejna, eik sawar apney peechey chhodney sey ziyada pasand hai."
1608,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : na-tamam (namukammal) bachcha apney Rab sey jhagda kerega (israr key sath shafaat kerega) jab uska Rab uskey waliden ko jahannam mein dakhil kerega. (uski us shafaat key natijey mein) usey kaha jaeyga : aey apney Rab sey jhagadney waley na-tamam (namukammal) bachchey ! apney maa baap ko jannat mein ley ja, chunanche wo unhen apni aanwal sey khinch kar jannat mein dakhil kar dega. Abu-Ali ney kaha : (یُرَاغِمُ رَبَّه), key maana hain (یُغَاضِبُ), ke wo apney rab sey narazi ka izhar kerega."
1609,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! na-tamam (namukammal) bacha apni maa ko aanval (naadi) key zariey sey khinch kar jannat mein ley jaeyga jabke usney is par sabr kiya ho."
1610,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Jaafar (bin Abi Talib) (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ki khabar aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jaafar key ghar walon key liye khana tayyar karo, unkey paas wo chiz aa gaee hai, ya farmaya : wo maamla aa gaya hai jisney unhen mashghool kar diya hai."
1611,"Hazrat Asma binte Umes (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) shaheed huye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar walon key paas tashrif ley gaey aur farmaya : Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar waley marhoom ki wajeh sey mashghool hain (gham ki wajeh sey khana waghera tayyar karney ki taraf tawajjoh nahin kar saktey), tum log unkey liye khana tayyar karo. Abdullah bin Abi Bakr (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye tariqa jari raha yahan tak key wo fakhr aur mubaahaat (shaikhi) aur shohrat ka sabab bin gaya, chunanche isey tarak kar diya gaya."
1612,"Hazrat Jareer bin Abdullah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log maiyat walon key yahan jama honey ko aur (jama honey walon key liye) khana tayyar karney ko nauha shumar kartey they."
1613,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : be watni ki maut shahadat hai."
1614,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Madina main eik aadmi faut ho gaya, uski wiladat bhi Madina mein hui thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska janaza padhaya aur farmaya : kaash! ! wo apney maqame paidaish key siwa (kisi aur maqam par) faut hota. haazirin mein sey eik sahab ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (aap ye tamanna) kyon (kar rahey hain)? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab aadmi apni paidaish ki jagah key ilawa kisi aur maqam par faut hota hai to uskey liye maqame paidaish sey maqame wafat tak pemaaish kar key (uskey barabar jagah) jannat mein di jati hai."
1615,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs bimar ho kar mara, wo shaheed huwa, usey qabr key azab sey mehfooz rakha jaeyga aur usey subah aur Sham jannat sey rizq diya jata hai."
1616,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : maiyat ki haddi todnaa aisey hi hai, jaisey uski zindagi mein todnaa."
1617,"Hazrat Ummul-mominin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : murdey ki haddi todnaa gunah key lihaz sey aisa hi hai jaisey zinda ki haddi todnaa."
1618,"Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah bin Aqba (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey istifsaar (sawal) kartey huye kaha : Ummi jaan ! mujhey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key (qurbe wafat) marz key mutalliq bataaiye. unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar ho gaey. aap phunk maarney lagey. hum aap ki phunk ko munaqqaa khaney waley ki phunk sey tashbih detey they. aap baari baari azwaje-mutahrat (paak biwiyon) key yahan iqaamat farmatey they. jab aap ziyada bimar ho gaey to paak biwiyon sey ijazat talab ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khud Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key ghar mein thehrey rahen aur azwaaje mutah'raat (paak biwiyan) apni apni baari par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hoti rahen. ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do aadmiyon key darmiyan (un key saharey sey chaltey huye) merey ghar mein dakhil huye aur (zauf ki wajeh sey) aap key qadam Mubarak zamin par lakeer banatey aa rahey they. un do hazraat mein sey eik Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) they. (Ubedullah (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke) mainey ye hadees Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) key samney bayan ki. unhoney farmaya : kya aap ko malum hai ke wo doosrey sahab kon they jinka Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ney naam nahin liya? wo Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) they."
1619,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) in alfaz key sath Allah ki panah hasil kartey they : (أَذْهِبِ الْبَاسَ رَبَّ النَّاسِ . وَاشْفِ أَنْتَ الشَّافِى لاَ شِفَاءَ إِلاَّ شِفَاؤُكَ شِفَاءً لاَ يُغَادِرُ سَقَمًا), ''aey insanon key Rab ! bimari door kar dey aur shifa dey dey to hi shifa deney wala hai, teri shifa key siwa koi shifa nahin, aisi shifa ata farma jo bimari ko bilkul baqi na chhodey.'' jis bimari mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui, uskey doran mein jab tabiyat ziyada na saaz ho gaee to main ye dua padhti aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath pakad kar aap key jism par pherti thi. (hayaate mubaraka key aakhiri din jab mainey dam karna chah (to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna haath Mubarak merey haath sey nikal liya aur farmaya : (اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْلِى وَأَلْحِقْنِى بِالرَّفِيقِ الأَعْلَى), ''aey Allah ! meri maghfirat farma aur mujhey buland martaba sathiyon sey mila dey. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : ye aakhiri alfaz hain jo mainey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak sey suney."
1620,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : jo bhi Nabi bimar hota hai, usey duniya aur aakhirat mein sey eik chiz key intikhaab ka ikhtiyar diya jata hai. Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par wo bimari aai jis mein aap ki wafat hui (us doran main eik dafa) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aawaz bhari ho gaee. mainey suna to aap farma rahey they : (مَعَ الَّذِينَ أَنْعَمَ اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِمْ مِنَ النَّبِيِّينَ وَالصِّدِّيقِينَ وَالشُّهَدَاءِ وَالصَّالِحِينَ),''un logon key sath jin par Allah ney inaamat nazil kiye hain, Nabiyon, Siddiqon, shaheedon aur nek logon mein sey.''tab mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wo ikhtiyar dey diya gaya hai."
1621,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : (eik baar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaje mutah'raat (paak biwiyan) Raziallahu anhu anhunna (eik jagah) jama thin, un mein sey koi bhi ghair hazir na thi. (itney mein) Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) tashrif ley aayeen, un ki chaal Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki chaal sey intehai mushabeh thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : meri beti ko khush aamadeed. phir unhen apni baain taraf bitha liya aur chupkey sey unhen koi baat batai to Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) roney lagin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen phir chupkey sey koi baat batai to wo hans padin. mainey un sey kaha : aap ro kyon rahi thin? unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka raz zahir nahin kar sakti. mainey kaha : mainey kabhi is tarah gham key fauran baad khushi hasil hotey nahin dekhi jis tarah aaj dekhi hai. jab wo roin thin, to mainey un sey kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hum sab ko chhod kar aap sey khas tor par baat ki hai (ye to eik sharf aur khushi ki baat hai) phir bhi aap ro rahi hain? mainey un sey puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kya farmaya tha. unhoney kaha : main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka raz zahir nahin kar sakti. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to uskey baad (kisi munasib moqe par) mainey un sey (phir) poochh liya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kya farmaya tha. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujhey bata rahey they ke Hazrat Jibril (Alaihissalam) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath har saal eik baar Quran Majeed ka daur kiya kartey they, is saal do baar daur kiya hai (aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ) mera yehi khayal hai ke mera waqt qarib aa gaya hai aur merey gharaney mein sab sey pehley tum mujh sey milogi aur main tumhara behtar peshro hun. (ye sun kar) mujhey ronaa aa gaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mujh sey sar goshi mein farmaya : kya tum is baat sey khush nahin ho ke tum mominon ki aurton ki sardar ho? ya farmaya : ke tum is ummat ki aurton ki sardar ho? is (khushkhabri) ki wajeh sey mujhey hansi aa gaee."
1622,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ziyada kisi par takleef ki shiddat nahin dekhi."
1623,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha jabke aap ka aakhiri waqt tha. aap key paas pani ka eik piyala tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) piyaley mein haath daltey, phir pani (wala haath) chehrey par pher letey , phir farmatey : aey Allah ! maut ki sakhtiyon par meri madad farma."
1624,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey aakhiri baar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Chehrey Mubarak ki ziyaarat us waqt ki jab Somwar key din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key hujre mubaraka ka) parda hataayaa, meri nazar aap key Chehrey Mubarak par padi to wo yun mehsus ho raha tha goya Quran Majeed ka eik warq ho. (us waqt) log Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein namaze (Fajr) ada kar rahey they. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney (apni jagah sey) hatna chaha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ishara farmaya ke (wahin) khadey raho aur parda gira diya. isi din key aakhiri hissey mein aap ki wafat ho gaee."
1625,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke jis marz mein Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney intiqam farmaya, uskey doran mein aap farmaya kartey they : namaz (ki hifazat karo) aur (un londi ghulamon ki) jo tumharey haathon ki milkiyat hain. aap ney ye alfaz bar-bar farmaae yahan tak key aap ki zaban Mubarak ruk gaee."
1626,"Hazrat Aswad (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kuchh logon ney Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki mojudgi mein ye zikr kiya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) wasi they (Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unkey haq mein wasiyat ki thi). Ummul-mominin (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen kis waqt wasiyat ki? (jabke wafat key waqt) Rasoolullah ka sar Mubarak merey seeney par ya (farmaya) meri god mein tha (mainey in ko seeney ya god ka sahara diya huwa tha) aap ney bartan talab farmaya. (achchha) meri god hi mein aap ka jism Mubarak dhila pad gaya aur mujhey (rooh aqdas key parwaaz kar janey ka) ehsas bhi na huwa. phir aap ney wasiyat kis waqt ki?"
1627,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui, us waqt Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) awaali main apni zauja mohtarma (biwi) Khaarija ki beti key yahan tashrif farma they. baaz afrad ney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut nahin huye, ye to us sey milti julti kaifiyat hai, jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par nuzoole ""wahi"" key moqey par taari huwa karti thi. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye. unhoney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key Chehrey aqdas sey kapda hataayaa aur dono aakhon key darmiyan (peshaani Mubarak par) bosa diya aur farmaya : Allah key yahan aap ki shaan itni buland hai ke wo aap par do baar maut taari nahin karega. Allah ki qism ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey hain. (us waqt) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) masjid key eik hissey mein farma rahey they : qism hai Allah ki ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut nahin huye aur aap us waqt tak faut nahin hongey jab tak bahut sey munafiqon key haath paon nahin kaat detey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar member par chaley gaey aur farmaya : jo koi Allah ki ibadat karta tha to Allah Taala zinda hai, faut nahin huwa , aur jo koi Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ibadat karta tha to (uskey mabood) Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki to wafat ho gaee. (aur ye aayat padhi : )  (وَمَا مُحَمَّدٌ إِلاَّ رَسُولٌ قَدْ خَلَتْ مِنْ قَبْلِهِ الرُّسُلُ أَفَإِنْ مَاتَ أَوْ قُتِلَ انْقَلَبْتُمْ عَلَى أَعْقَابِكُمْ وَمَنْ يَنْقَلِبْ عَلَى عَقِبَيْهِ فَلَنْ يَضُرَّ اللَّهَ شَيْئًا وَسَيَجْزِى اللَّهُ الشَّاكِرِينَ),''aur Muhammad ((Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) sirf eik Rasool hain. is sey pehley bhi Rasool guzar chukey hain. to agar wo faut ho jaeyn ya shaheed ho jaeyn to kya tum ultey paon phir jaogey? aur jo koi ultey paon phireyga wo Allah ka kuch nuqsan nahin kerega. aur shukar guzaaron ko Allah jaza dega.'' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney (baad mein) farmaya : mujhey to (Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye aayat sun kar) yun mehsus huwa tha, goya mainey (ye aayat) isi din padhi hai. (goya pehley kabhi padhi ya suni hi nahin)."
1628,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jab Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye qabr tayyar karney ka irada kiya to Hazrat abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham bheja, wo Makka walon key riwaaj key mutabiq sanduqi (shaqq wali) qabr banatey they. aur Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi pegham bheja, wo Madina walon ki qabren tayyar kiya kartey they aur baghli (lahad wali) qabr banatey they. Sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum ney un dono hazraat ki taraf do (alag alag) aadmiyon ko bheja aur kaha : aey Allah ! apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye behtar surat mohaiyya farma . Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) mil gaey, unhen (qabr tayyar karney key liye) ley aaya gaya. Hazrat abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) (ghar par) na miley. chunanche Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye baghli (lahad wali) qabr tayyar ki. mangal key din jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tajheez aur takfeen sey faraaghat hui to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key jasad Mubarak) ko aap key hujre Mubarak mein aap ki chaarpai par litaa diya gayaa. log giroh dar giroh andar dakhil hotey they aur namaze janaza ada kartey. jab mard farigh ho gaey to khawatin ko dakhil honey ki ijazat di gaee. jab un sey faraaghat hui to bachchon ko andar janey ki ijazat di gaee. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki namaze janaza key liye kisi ney logon ki imaamat nahin ki. (uskey baad) musalmanon mein is mamley mein ikhtilaf raey pesh aaya key Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak kahan tayyar ki jaaey. kuchh hazraat ney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Masjide Nabawi mein dafn kiya jaey. kuchh hazraat ney kaha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney Sahaba key sath (baqeea' key qabristaan mein) dafn kiya jaey. Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye farman suna hai : jo bhi Nabi faut huwa , wo jahan faut huwa , wahin dafn huwa. chunanche Sahaba ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka wo bistar uthaya , jis par aap ki wafat hui thi, aur (us maqam par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qabr Mubarak tayyar ki, phir buddh ki raat , aadhi raat key waqt aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tadfeen amal mein aai. Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma), unkey bhai Hazrat Qusam (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Shuqran (Raziallahu anhu) qabr mein utrey. Hazrat Abu-Leila Aus bin Khauli (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap ko Allah ka wasta aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey hamarey talluq ka wasta ! Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : aap bhi (qabr mein) utar aayen. Hazrat Shuqran (Raziallahu anhu) Mola Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas wo chadar thi jo Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) odha kartey they. unhoney wo chadar bhi qabr mein dafn kar di aur kaha : Allah ki qism ! aap key baad ye chadar kabhi koi doosra shakhs istimal nahin karega, chunanche wo chadar Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath hi dafn hui."
1629,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wafat key waqt ghabrahat (ya takleef) mehsus hui to Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : haaye abba jaan ki takleef ! Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aaj key baad terey walid ko koi takleef nahin hogi ! terey walid ko wo chiz (maut) pesh aa gaee hai jis sey kisi ko chhutkaaraa nahin. qiyamat key roz mulaqat hogi."
1630,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mujhey Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : Anas ! tumharey dilon ney ye kaisey gawara kiya ke tum apney haathon sey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (key jasad at'har (jism)) par mitti dal do? Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney (mazeed) farmaya : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat hui to Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : haaye abba jaan ! main Jibril ko aap ki wafat ki khabar deti hun . haaye abba jaan ! aap ko apney Rab ka kitna qurb hasil hai. haaye abba jaan ! Jannatul-Firdaus aap ka thikana hai ! haaye abba jaan ! Rab ney aap ko bulaya aur aap ney uskey bulaawey par labbaik keh diya. Hammad bin Zaid (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke mainey (apney ustaad aur Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) key shagrid) Janab Sabit (Rahimahullah) ko dekha ke jab unhoney ye hadees bayan farmaai to bahut roey yahan tak key mujhey aap ki pasliyan ooper nichey hoti nazar aatin."
1631,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : jis din Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina Munawra mein tashrif farma huye, uski har chiz roshan ho gaee aur jis din aap ki wafat hui, Madina ki har chiz taareek (andheri) ho gaee. hamney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dafn kar key apney haath jhaadey to usi waqt hamein apney dilon ki haalat badli hui mehsus hui."
1632,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein hum apni aurton sey baat kartey huye aur be-takallufi ka izhar kartey huye bhi dartey they, is dar sey ke Quran (mein hamari kisi ghalati par tanbih waala farman) nazil ho jaeyga. jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to hum (har qism ki) baaten karney lagey (us darjey ki ehtiyat na rahi)."
1633,"Hazrat Ubai-bin Kaab (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein hum logon ki tawajjoh eik hi (aakhirat ki) taraf hoti thi, jab aap faut ho gaey to idhar-udhar (koi duniya ko aur koi aakhirat ko) dekhney lagey."
1634,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma (biwi) Hazrat Umme-Salma bint Abu Umayya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key ehad Mubarak mein logon ki ye haalat thi ke jab aadmi namaz padhney khada hota to uski nazar qadmon sey aagey na badhti jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to logon ki ye haalat ho gaee ke jab koi shakhs namaz padhney khada hota to uski nazar uski peshani rakhney ki jagah (sajdey ki jagah) sey aagey nahin badhti thi, phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) (khalifa) muqarrar ho gaey to logon ki ye haalat ho gaee ke jab koi shakhs namaz padhney khada hota to uski nigah qibley ki taraf sey nahin hat'ti thi, phir Hazrat Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) (khalifa) muqarrar huye to (un key doore hukumat mein) fitna barpa huwa aur (fitney key us door mein) log (namaz mein) daain baain jhaankne lagey."
1635,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key wafaat farma janey key baad (eik baar) Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : chaliye Hazrat Umme Aiman (Raziallahu anha) key yahan chalen aur un sey mulaqat kar ayen jis tarah Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un sey mulaqat key liye tashrif ley jaya kartey they. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : jab hum log un ki khidmat mein hazir huye to wo (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko yad kar key) aasunon se bhar gaeen. dono hazraat ney farmaya : aap kyon ro rahi hain? Allah key paas jo kuchh hai wo uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye (duniya ki daulat aur aasaaishon sey kahin) behtar hai. Umme Aiman (Raziallahu anha) ney farmaya : ye to main bhi jaanti hun ke Allah key paas jo kuchh hai wo uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye behtar hai lekin main to isliye roti hun ke (Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat sey) aasman sey ""wahi"" aana band ho gaee hai. un ki is baat sey Shekhain (Raziallahu anhuma) ko bhi ronaa aa gaya aur wo bhi roney lagey."
1636,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey ka din tumharey afzal dinon mein sey hai. isi mein Adam (Alaihissalam) ki takhleeq hui, isi din soor phunka jaeyga, isi din (qiyamat ki) be-hoshi hogi, lihaza is din mujh par kasrat sey durood padha karo kyonkey tumhara durood mujh par pesh kiya jata hai. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! jab aap ka jasad at'har (jism Mubarak) khaak ho jaeyga tab hamara durood kaisey aap par pesh kiya jaeyga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ney zamin par haram kar diya hai ke wo nabiyon key jismon ko khaye."
1637,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Jumey key din mujh par durood ziyada padha karo, is mein farishtey hazir hotey hain aur jo shakhs bhi mujh par durood padhega to uskey farigh honey tak uska durood merey samney pesh kiya jata rahega. mainey arz kiya : aur wafat key baad? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aur wafat key baad bhi (aisey hi hoga) Allah ney zamin par haram kar diya hai ke wo nabiyon key jismon ko khaye, chunanche Allah ka Nabi zinda hota hai, usey rizq milta hai."
